race.comment: BRAVE MONARCH (1) got the maiden win out of the way last time out and will have derived a stack of confidence from that victory. Winning rider Harley sticks in the saddle and another strong showing would not surprise. PROVOKER (3) has placed two from two around this circuit and should be able to sit up on speed from the inside marble. Will give backers a sight. MEET GEORGE (2) is one from one over this seven-furlong journey and strips fitter third-up from the break. Hard to beat in this suitable race. WANTED HILLBILLY (4) has only missed the top-four once in seven career outings and looks one for the exotics players. HOSTILE LA VISTA (6) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be slept on.
